href="http://www.gurusblog.com">GurusBlog</a>.</p></p>]]></content:encoded> <wfw:commentRss>http://www.gurusblog.com/archives/banca-dta-bonos/23/11/2013/feed/</wfw:commentRss> <slash:comments>2</slash:comments> </item> <item><title>Y mientras en Grecia&#8230;.La troika deja Grecia sin acuerdo para desbloquear un nuevo tramo del rescate</title><link>http://www.gurusblog.com/archives/troika-deja-grecia-sin-acuerdo-rescate/21/11/2013/</link> <comments>http://www.gurusblog.com/archives/troika-deja-grecia-sin-acuerdo-rescate/21/11/2013/#comments</comments> <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2013 11:45:40 +0000</pubDate> <dc:creator><![CDATA[Guru Huky]]></dc:creator> <category><![CDATA[Confidencial]]></category> <category><![CDATA[LVA]]></category> <category><![CDATA[Portada]]></category> <category><![CDATA[euro]]></category> <category><![CDATA[grecia]]></category> <category><![CDATA[Troika]]></category> <category><![CDATA[UE]]></category><guid
